Coronavirus guidance is being updated.
Read what you can and cannot do

Coronavirus restrictions
Visiting vessel permits for yachts will not be issued until further notice. If you have applied or have been issued permits you will be contacted separately. If you have any questions, contact biotadmin@fco.gov.uk. See also Staying during coronavirus.
Regular entry requirements
Permits
Access to the British Indian Ocean Territory is restricted and a permit is required in advance of travel. There are no commercial flights.
Passport validity
Your passport must be valid for a minimum period of 6 months from the date of entry into British Indian Ocean Territory.
